話同你講野....<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"03668baeaa54316abd16c940afb0c089d835ebfc","tid":147701,"uid":1025,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-08T19:36:20.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>例如日本/歐洲/美國直航返香港咁<br />\n空姐見你似香港人就講廣東話?定直接全部英文</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n通常亞洲樣都係講廣東話先<br />\n如果佢地唔識廳先會用返英文<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/12.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"67c7a15d04fe4891e1215abe5ffddcd4a7d48400","tid":147701,"uid":33053,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-08T19:50:07.000Z","msg":"我搭CX都係講廣東話喎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4d84eaf8abfe601209e4c0bbf26881813d5ab021","tid":147701,"uid":40360,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-08T20:13:37.000Z","msg":"搭CX試過比空姐用德文問我飲咩.....點知我答完佢佢反而聽唔明.....跟住佢好尷尬咁用翻廣東話問我想飲乜<br />\n<br />\nZRH-HKG"},{"pid":"f0065420fb67733acd368af7a81f56e38e36c5ed","tid":147701,"uid":44678,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-08T20:17:46.000Z","msg":"睇你個zone咩人多，所以boarding 好重要，會留意你講咩語言，但通常香港人面孔都係講英文，因聽得明"},{"pid":"6d3da02d7484a249676a6511ff83eec9b05370ea","tid":147701,"uid":89823,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-08T20:45:23.000Z","msg":"成日坐CX來回香港同紐約<br />\n次次都好多蝗又成日坐喺啲蝗附近<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n啲空姐成q日同我講蝗語<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cb4861e97a3ec4f0805e0153215ce9d0614e06ea","tid":147701,"uid":43964,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-08T22:46:52.000Z","msg":"英文，多數係英文😉"},{"pid":"6221517144d7f6cf46366087a0635348c650fe1b","tid":147701,"uid":18959,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-08T23:00:13.000Z","msg":"空姐會同我講英文"},{"pid":"59a39a75cf38ac57c1