 />\n啲空姐成q日同我講蝗語<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n用返廣東話 或英文答佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n成機蝗佢會當埋你係蝗，我會堅持同佢講英文"}]}